sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Istio as Istio Sidecar<br/>15006/TCP mTLS
    participant Server as AutoGluon Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Tabular as TabularPredictor<br/>(in-process)
    participant TimeSeries as TimeSeriesPredictor<br/>(in-process)
    participant Storage as kserve-storage<br/>(in-process)
    participant S3 as S3/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Model Loading from Storage (startup)
    Storage->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / GCP SA
    S3-->>Storage: Model artifacts
    Storage->>Server: Write to /mnt/models
    Server->>Server: predictor_detect.py<br/>Auto-detect model type
    alt TimeSeriesPredictor detected
        Server->>TimeSeries: TimeSeriesPredictor.load()
    else TabularPredictor detected
        Server->>Tabular: TabularPredictor.load()
    end

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Tabular Inference (v2 Open Inference Protocol)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token or mTLS
    Gateway->>Istio: Forward request<br/>TLS terminated
    Istio->>Server: HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS STRICT (mesh internal)
    Server->>Server: Parse v2 tensor inputs<br/>Map to DataFrame columns
    Server->>Tabular: predict(DataFrame)
    Tabular-->>Server: Predictions array
    Server->>Server: Format v2 InferResponse<br/>(named output tensors)
    Server-->>Istio: JSON Response
    Istio-->>Gateway: mTLS
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Time Series Forecasting (v1 REST)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token or mTLS
    Gateway->>Istio: Forward request<br/>TLS terminated
    Istio->>Server: HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS STRICT (mesh internal)
    Server->>Server: Parse v1 JSON instances<br/>Build TimeSeriesDataFrame
    Server->>TimeSeries: predict(TimeSeriesDataFrame)
    TimeSeries-->>Server: Forecast results
    Server->>Server: Format v1 JSON predictions
    Server-->>Istio: JSON Response
    Istio-->>Gateway: mTLS
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: gRPC Inference (v2 OIP)
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC ModelInfer<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>Istio: Forward
    Istio->>Server: gRPC/8081<br/>mTLS
    Server->>Tabular: predict(DataFrame)
    Tabular-->>Server: Predictions
    Server-->>Istio: gRPC InferResponse
    Istio-->>Gateway: mTLS
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC Response
